443
00:20:59,690 --> 00:21:00,370
You...

444
00:21:01,350 --> 00:21:03,000
Shameless!

445
00:21:03,030 --> 00:21:04,380
Shame on you!

446
00:21:04,430 --> 00:21:05,230
Shame on you!

447
00:21:05,230 --> 00:21:06,400
Shame on you!

448
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,110
Shame on you!

449
00:21:07,110 --> 00:21:08,750
-Shame on you!
