00:21:08,750 --> 00:21:09,230
Stop.

451
00:21:21,120 --> 00:21:21,890
Kneel!

452
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:24,050
Xu Xin,

453
00:21:24,800 --> 00:21:25,750
you betrayed us and submitted to our enemy,

454
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:26,990
