455
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:30,370
Now all members of the Xu family have been executed.

456
00:21:30,430 --> 00:21:31,960
What else do you have to say?

457
00:21:32,270 --> 00:21:32,970
Xu Xin.

458
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:36,140
Duan Yan.

459
00:21:38,130 --> 00:21:39,230
I didn't expect

460
00:21:39,280 --> 00:21:42,210
Xu Xin has submitted to the Sacred Blood Sect.

461
00:21:42,340 --> 00:21:44,610
The Sacred Blood Sect is so rampant.

462
00:21:45,250 --> 00:21:46,480
We don't know

463
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:48,440
