484
00:22:30,840 --> 00:22:32,420
That's why it's important.

485
00:22:33,060 --> 00:22:35,230
You must take it seriously.

486
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:39,430
Xing Si,

487
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:41,300
