587
00:26:43,590 --> 00:26:44,630
Go ahead.

588
00:26:47,150 --> 00:26:48,690
I don't want to marry Duan Yu.

589
00:26:48,690 --> 00:26:49,780
Nonsense!

590
00:26:50,130 --> 00:26:52,410
How can you take the arrangement of parents

591
00:26:52,410 --> 00:26:54,550
and match-makers as a joke?

592
00:26:54,630 --> 00:26:56,500
Duan Yu just broke off the engagement,

593
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:58,230
and now you refuse to marry him.

594
00:26:58,440 --> 00:27:00,040
Have you all lost your minds?

595
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:00,720
Father,

596
00:27:00,920 --> 00:27:02,320
I've thought it through.

597
00:27:02,570 --> 00:27:04,470
Duan Yu has never liked me.

598
00:27:04,560 --> 00:27:06,560
Even if I marry him, I won't be happy.

599
00:27:06,560 --> 00:27:07,710
If we're not going to be happy together,

600
00:27:07,710 --> 00:27:09,240
why should I marry him?

601
00:27:10,630 --> 00:27:11,890
Since when did you start

602
00:27:11,890 --> 00:27:13,890
talking about love affairs

603
00:27:13,900 --> 00:27:15,960
like those common folk?

604
00:27:15,990 --> 00:27:17,460
Even if you beat me to death,

605
00:27:17,460 --> 00:27:18,780
I won't marry him.

606
00:27:18,810 --> 00:27:19,530
Fine.

607
00:27:20,190 --> 00:27:22,410
Since you're determined,

608
00:27:22,800 --> 00:27:24,400
I'll respect your decision.

609
00:27:26,310 --> 00:27:28,240
Today, the marriage is cancelled,

610
00:27:28,420 --> 00:27:31,390
the Du and Duan family are no longer friends.

611
00:27:31,820 --> 00:27:32,560
Young Master,

612
00:27:32,560 --> 00:27:34,850
isn't it hard to explain to our master?

613
00:27:34,950 --> 00:27:37,230
We are different from the Du family.

614
00:27:37,650 --> 00:27:40,110
I will explain it to my brother myself.

615
00:27:40,150 --> 00:27:41,210
What about Miss Du?

616
00:27:41,430 --> 00:27:43,350
She truly has feelings for you.

617
00:27:44,510 --> 00:27:45,880
It's my fault she got involved.

618
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:46,630
Should I

619
00:27:47,050 --> 00:27:49,050
go and talk to her?

620
00:27:49,080 --> 00:27:50,280
If you go to her now,

621
00:27:50,310 --> 00:27:51,900
it will only hurt her more.

622
00:27:53,550 --> 00:27:54,540
Master Ruan,

623
00:27:55,580 --> 00:27:58,540
I know it's impossible between Duan Yu and me.

624
00:27:59,020 --> 00:28:00,690
In the remaining days,

625
00:28:01,320 --> 00:28:02,990
I just want to repay him

626
00:28:03,020 --> 00:28:04,780
for his trust and help.

627
00:28:06,060 --> 00:28:06,790
I know,

628
00:28:07,610 --> 00:28:08,820
for me,

629
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:10,880
the most important thing is

630
00:28:11,040 --> 00:28:14,610
to find the Four Treasures and return to my original world.

631
00:28:16,180 --> 00:28:16,940
My Lady,

632
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:20,020
dinner is ready.

633
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:21,590
Coming.

634
00:28:22,790 --> 00:28:24,190
I'm going to have dinner.

635
00:29:10,080 --> 00:29:11,640
This Soul-stealing Nail

636
00:29:11,670 --> 00:29:14,130
can temporarily seal your spiritual power.

637
00:29:14,710 --> 00:29:15,940
In this way,

638
00:29:17,050 --> 00:29:19,460
I can rest assured and leave.

639
00:29:22,360 --> 00:29:23,730
Xu Xin has died.

640
00:29:23,860 --> 00:29:26,060
This is the treasure map he left behind.

641
00:29:27,120 --> 00:29:27,860
Very good.

642
00:29:27,890 --> 00:29:29,890
There are three more treasure maps.

643
00:29:31,180 --> 00:29:33,210
I'll get one of them myself.

644
00:29:33,320 --> 00:29:35,010
The Star of Rebellion is dying.

645
00:29:35,010 --> 00:29:37,730
We must gather the Four Treasures before she dies.

646
00:29:37,730 --> 00:29:39,050
If she dies,

647
00:29:39,560 --> 00:29:41,200
there is no turning back.

648
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:42,930
Time is running out.

649
00:29:43,180 --> 00:29:44,380
Do whatever it takes.

650
00:29:48,950 --> 00:29:50,610
Welcome, please go upstairs.

651
00:29:52,940 --> 00:29:53,510
This way.

652
00:29:56,640 --> 00:29:57,700
Mind the steps.

653
00:30:08,080 --> 00:30:08,710
Master.

654
00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:11,250
Tell me.

655
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:12,460
Who are you?

656
00:30:12,490 --> 00:30:13,540
Destiny calls.

657
00:30:13,560 --> 00:30:15,960
The Sacred Blood Sect will return.

658
00:30:22,870 --> 00:30:23,580
Master,

659
00:30:23,760 --> 00:30:25,190
the rest of them committed suicide.

660
00:30:25,190 --> 00:30:26,190
No survivors.

661
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:28,770
These disciples of Sacred Blood Sect are fearless of death,

662
00:30:28,770 --> 00:30:30,830
just like the people of the Xu family.

663
00:30:31,050 --> 00:30:32,330
It's really tricky.

664
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:34,030
Fortunately, you had predicted

665
00:30:34,030 --> 00:30:35,750
