666
00:30:35,900 --> 00:30:36,930
Well,

667
00:30:37,170 --> 00:30:38,930
if I could be ambushed,

668
00:30:38,950 --> 00:30:41,870
then Great Master Zhang and Principal Cheng are no exception.

669
00:30:41,870 --> 00:30:43,220
Great Master Zhang is a skilled martial artist,

670
00:30:43,220 --> 00:30:44,820
so I'm not worried about him.

671
00:30:45,310 --> 00:30:47,000
But Principal Cheng is weak and sick,

672
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:48,440
which concerns me.

673
00:30:48,470 --> 00:30:49,640
You mean...

674
00:30:49,660 --> 00:30:50,620
Detour to Jizhou

675
00:30:50,650 --> 00:30:52,850
to prevent any harm to Principal Cheng.

676
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:54,950
Qiao.

677
00:30:56,860 --> 00:30:57,590
The Du family

678
00:30:58,430 --> 00:30:59,890
broke off the engagement.

679
00:31:00,710 --> 00:31:01,660
You know

680
00:31:02,150 --> 00:31:04,480
it's impossible between me and Du Ruoyun.

681
00:31:06,530 --> 00:31:07,350
Qiao,

682
00:31:07,590 --> 00:31:08,790
I just want to grow old

683
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,060
together with you.

684
00:31:11,630 --> 00:31:12,440
Duan Yu,

685
00:31:13,160 --> 00:31:15,290
I don't want to make decisions for you,

686
00:31:15,970 --> 00:31:17,230
but one day,

687
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:19,830
you'll find someone who truly loves you.

688
00:31:19,980 --> 00:31:20,810
That person

689
00:31:21,810 --> 00:31:22,500
is not me.

690
00:31:25,180 --> 00:31:26,440
I've thought about it.

691
00:31:27,150 --> 00:31:30,500
I'm willing to follow you to your world.

692
00:31:30,670 --> 00:31:31,630
What?

693
00:31:31,660 --> 00:31:32,510
You said that

694
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:34,540
we're not from the same world,

695
00:31:34,660 --> 00:31:36,030
so we can't be together.

696
00:31:36,470 --> 00:31:38,100
If I go to your world,

697
00:31:39,050 --> 00:31:41,730
everything will be fine.

698
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:44,090
Alright.

699
00:31:45,120 --> 00:31:46,520
Let's not talk about this

700
00:31:46,730 --> 00:31:47,370
Qiao,

701
00:31:47,830 --> 00:31:49,130
since you could come here,

702
00:31:49,130 --> 00:31:50,530
surely I can go there too.

703
00:31:50,790 --> 00:31:53,120
This miracle won't only happen once.

704
00:31:53,310 --> 00:31:53,980
Duan Yu,

705
00:31:54,370 --> 00:31:55,770
I've thought it through.

706
00:31:57,270 --> 00:32:00,580
I came here by accident

707
00:32:01,110 --> 00:32:02,030
and a mistake.

708
00:32:02,730 --> 00:32:04,130
If I hadn't come here,

709
00:32:04,430 --> 00:32:06,950
we wouldn't have had to go through this.

710
00:32:07,110 --> 00:32:08,550
You wouldn't have been hurt,

711
00:32:08,550 --> 00:32:12,030
and Master Ruan wouldn't...

712
00:32:12,630 --> 00:32:13,270
So...

713
00:32:13,270 --> 00:32:15,550
So none of this is your fault.

714
00:32:15,550 --> 00:32:16,750
Don't think that way.

715
00:32:16,930 --> 00:32:18,590
So after I leave,

716
00:32:19,490 --> 00:32:21,540
I want your life to return to normal.

717
00:32:21,890 --> 00:32:23,210
That's what I hope for.

718
00:32:30,510 --> 00:32:31,990
In my world,

719
00:32:32,070 --> 00:32:34,370
the boy with the same name as you

720
00:32:34,500 --> 00:32:36,330
also likes inventing creation.

721
00:32:37,770 --> 00:32:39,600
When he was in eighth grade,

722
00:32:39,630 --> 00:32:42,160
he even won a young inventor's championship.

723
00:32:48,580 --> 00:32:49,870
Shaoyi?

724
00:32:51,260 --> 00:32:52,340
Could it be you?

725
00:32:53,930 --> 00:32:54,730
What's wrong?

726
00:33:02,220 --> 00:33:04,650
Why did you call us in such a hurry?

727
00:33:05,110 --> 00:33:06,090
What happened?

728
00:33:06,600 --> 00:33:07,640
Speak up,

729
00:33:07,890 --> 00:33:08,920
don't keep us guessing.

730
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:10,320
I have a bold idea.

731
00:33:10,810 --> 00:33:12,410
The last Spiritual Treasure

732
00:33:12,600 --> 00:33:13,800
might be with Shaoyi.

733
00:33:14,460 --> 00:33:15,500
Me?

734
00:33:15,940 --> 00:33:17,300
Why didn't I know?

735
00:33:17,660 --> 00:33:18,950
I thought about it.

736
00:33:19,180 --> 00:33:20,380
In this world,

737
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:22,450
only the three of you and Master Ruan

738
00:33:22,480 --> 00:33:24,540
are people I knew from my modern life.

739
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:27,190
Black Wood Human-shaped Sword and Nine-turn Melodious Bell

740
00:33:27,190 --> 00:33:28,760
were originally mine.

741
00:33:28,870 --> 00:33:31,250
Lu Zizheng gave me the Nine-turn Melodious Bell.

742
00:33:31,250 --> 00:33:33,830
Master Ruan gave me the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

743
00:33:33,830 --> 00:33:34,990
Another Spiritual Treasure

744
00:33:34,990 --> 00:33:37,390
was found by Duan Yu in the Fire Crane Tribe.

745
00:33:37,580 --> 00:33:39,850
The last Spiritual Treasure

746
00:33:40,810 --> 00:33:42,080
should be with Shaoyi.

747
00:33:42,490 --> 00:33:44,030
That makes sense.

748
00:33:44,550 --> 00:33:45,750
Young Master Shaoyi,

749
00:33:45,830 --> 00:33:47,150
you need to check

750
00:33:47,190 --> 00:33:49,510
your belongings for something unusual.

751
00:33:49,600 --> 00:33:52,260
But the problem is I have too many unusual items,

752
00:33:52,270 --> 00:33:53,800
all quite rare in the world.

753
00:33:54,100 --> 00:33:55,170
How can I find it?

754
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:57,200
Then take out everything.

755
00:33:57,260 --> 00:33:59,180
Young Master Shaoyi has so many

756
00:33:59,200 --> 00:34:00,830
strange items.

757
00:34:01,410 --> 00:34:03,230
We've been moving for so long.

758
00:34:03,350 --> 00:34:05,120
Ruoyi, check

759
00:34:05,190 --> 00:34:06,590
how many are left?

760
00:34:06,930 --> 00:34:08,050
At least half.

761
00:34:08,080 --> 00:34:09,310
Half?

762
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:11,389
Oh my god.

763
00:34:11,409 --> 00:34:13,679
I spent a lot of money to get these treasures.

764
00:34:13,679 --> 00:34:15,420
Be careful not to damage them.

765
00:34:16,050 --> 00:34:18,409
I can't believe this.

766
00:34:18,500 --> 00:34:19,690
Are you Doraemon?

767
00:34:19,940 --> 00:34:21,110
What is Doraemon?

768
00:34:22,310 --> 00:34:24,440
It doesn't matter, just keep looking.

769
00:34:24,850 --> 00:34:25,570
Qiao.

770
00:34:28,650 --> 00:34:29,469
Miss Gu.

771
00:34:33,100 --> 00:34:34,810
There is a golden pig here.

772
00:34:35,270 --> 00:34:36,679
Heavenly Pearl?

773
00:34:37,719 --> 00:34:39,179
It should be a round thing.

774
00:34:39,179 --> 00:34:40,699
You've got some brains after all.

775
00:34:40,699 --> 00:34:42,449
I just thought of it.

776
00:34:42,820 --> 00:34:43,580
Qiao,

777
00:34:43,620 --> 00:34:45,060
could this be it?

778
00:34:45,080 --> 00:34:45,850
Impossible.

779
00:34:45,969 --> 00:34:46,980
This is football.

780
00:34:47,020 --> 00:34:48,090
Si made it for me.

781
00:34:48,120 --> 00:34:49,850
It can't be the Heavenly Pearl.

782
00:34:53,270 --> 00:34:54,080
What's wrong?

783
00:34:55,909 --> 00:34:56,969
Duan Shaoyi.

784
00:34:57,710 --> 00:34:58,660
What is this?

785
00:34:58,690 --> 00:34:59,730
When did I buy it?

786
00:34:59,780 --> 00:35:00,600
It doesn't matter.

787
00:35:00,600 --> 00:35:01,390
Take it away!

788
00:35:09,590 --> 00:35:11,830
Why isn't it any of these?

789
00:35:13,790 --> 00:35:14,700
Master Ruan,

790
00:35:15,660 --> 00:35:19,450
what do you think the Heavenly Pearl is?

791
00:35:25,350 --> 00:35:28,110
Why are you so quiet these days?

792
00:35:35,380 --> 00:35:36,430
Lu Zizheng.

793
00:35:38,140 --> 00:35:38,990
Lu Zizheng.

794
00:35:40,650 --> 00:35:41,570
He's not here.

795
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:51,430
I have to go now.

796
00:35:51,790 --> 00:35:52,780
Don't miss me too much.

797
00:35:52,780 --> 00:35:54,420
So narcissistic.

798
00:35:54,750 --> 00:35:56,350
Didn't say where he's going.

799
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:58,100
So mysterious.

800
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:00,790
My Lord.

801
00:36:02,740 --> 00:36:03,260
Say it.

802
00:36:03,490 --> 00:36:04,600
As you expected,

803
00:36:04,910 --> 00:36:06,490
Duan Yan discovered the assassination

804
00:36:06,490 --> 00:36:07,560
and is now heading to Jizhou

805
00:36:07,560 --> 00:36:08,580
to meet with Cheng Mufei.

806
00:36:08,580 --> 00:36:09,340
Good.

807
00:36:09,620 --> 00:36:11,380
We don't have much time left.

808
00:36:11,990 --> 00:36:14,520
It's better to catch them all at once than one by one.

809
00:36:14,520 --> 00:36:15,160
My Lord,

810
00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:16,470
are you going to Jizhou?

811
00:36:16,470 --> 00:36:16,950
No,

812
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:18,330
to Xiling.

813
00:36:18,610 --> 00:36:21,770
I need to solve some things myself.

814
00:36:24,410 --> 00:36:25,700
Gu Qingqiao,

815
00:36:26,070 --> 00:36:27,470
I want you to see

816
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:29,720
who can

817
00:36:29,750 --> 00:36:32,030
get the Heavenly Pearl first

818
00:36:32,940 --> 00:36:35,260
to open gate of time and space?

819
00:36:44,190 --> 00:36:44,810
Shaoyi.

820
00:36:46,180 --> 00:36:46,790
What's wrong?

821
00:36:46,790 --> 00:36:48,790
I want to study in Jizhou Academy.

822
00:36:49,290 --> 00:36:49,930
Why?

823
00:36:49,950 --> 00:36:51,650
I haven't been sleeping well lately.

824
00:36:51,650 --> 00:36:53,180
I keep dreaming of Wu.

825
00:36:53,350 --> 00:36:55,050
I want to stay somewhere else.

826
00:36:55,080 --> 00:36:55,710
Okay.

827
00:36:56,380 --> 00:36:58,630
Too many things have happened recently.

828
00:36:58,630 --> 00:37:02,150
You should go and clear your mind.

829
00:37:02,540 --> 00:37:05,370
[Xiling Sect]

830
00:37:04,460 --> 00:37:05,260
Senior,

831
00:37:05,750 --> 00:37:07,950
