832
00:37:08,030 --> 00:37:09,030
I don't know.

833
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:12,070
Great Master asked us to strengthen our defense as soon as he came back.

834
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:12,800
Senior,

835
00:37:12,950 --> 00:37:14,420
