00:37:33,060 --> 00:37:33,690
What's going on?

843
00:37:33,690 --> 00:37:35,570
Master, look who is back.

844
00:37:37,090 --> 00:37:38,260
Bai?

845
00:37:38,610 --> 00:37:39,250
Master,

846
00:37:39,330 --> 00:37:40,710
