847
00:37:48,730 --> 00:37:49,700
Bai,

848
00:37:50,070 --> 00:37:51,800
I miss you so much.

849
00:37:55,080 --> 00:37:57,220
Bai, long time no see.

850
00:37:57,350 --> 00:37:58,540
How are you?

851
00:37:58,850 --> 00:37:59,730
I'm fine.

852
00:37:59,890 --> 00:38:00,770
What about you?

853
00:38:00,870 --> 00:38:02,430
I'm fine.

854
00:38:02,450 --> 00:38:03,850
Everything is fine.

855
00:38:06,160 --> 00:38:06,960
Master,

856
00:38:07,250 --> 00:38:08,420
it was my fault.

857
00:38:08,740 --> 00:38:10,140
By the time I knew,

858
00:38:10,190 --> 00:38:11,150
