859
00:38:11,210 --> 00:38:13,710
It's not entirely your fault.

860
00:38:13,740 --> 00:38:15,750
You were also wronged.

861
00:38:16,100 --> 00:38:16,850
Alright,

862
00:38:17,110 --> 00:38:18,830
let's not stand here and talk.

863
00:38:19,960 --> 00:38:20,760
Let's go back.

864
00:38:21,110 --> 00:38:21,590
Go.

865
00:38:28,160 --> 00:38:30,490
Greetings, Great Master.

866
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:34,550
Rise.

867
00:38:37,480 --> 00:38:39,670
