870
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:44,060
Lu Zizheng.

871
00:38:44,090 --> 00:38:45,100
I remember

872
00:38:45,400 --> 00:38:48,320
Siqiong expelled you from the sect.

873
00:38:48,340 --> 00:38:50,380
