00:38:50,410 --> 00:38:52,120
Why did you come back now?

875
00:38:52,170 --> 00:38:52,930
Master,

876
00:38:53,240 --> 00:38:54,560
why do you ask that?

877
00:38:56,500 --> 00:38:59,120
If I expel you from the sect,

878
00:38:59,450 --> 00:39:01,090
won't you hate me?

879
00:39:01,110 --> 00:39:02,430
Not really.

880
00:39:02,730 --> 00:39:04,250
I might hold a grudge.

881
00:39:04,830 --> 00:39:05,590
Yeah.

882
00:39:05,750 --> 00:39:09,420
Even someone as honest as you would hold grudges.

883
00:39:10,110 --> 00:39:12,630
Is it wrong for me to ask why

884
00:39:13,340 --> 00:39:15,650
someone falsely accused of murder

885
00:39:16,420 --> 00:39:17,620
can return so calmly?

886
00:39:18,590 --> 00:39:19,940
Great Master is right.

887
00:39:20,110 --> 00:39:21,260
I do hate.

888
00:39:21,750 --> 00:39:22,790
Bai.

889
00:39:23,270 --> 00:39:24,460
But even I

890
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:27,120
can't always make the right judgement,

891
00:39:27,300 --> 00:39:29,950
not to mention Master Ruan who lost his disciple.

892
00:39:29,950 --> 00:39:30,750
Great Master,

893
00:39:31,130 --> 00:39:32,860
actually, I came to bring news.

894
00:39:33,130 --> 00:39:34,000
What news?

895
00:39:34,030 --> 00:39:35,660
I saw the Sword Spirit of Master Ruan.

896
00:39:35,660 --> 00:39:37,300
His Sword Spirit?

897
00:39:38,040 --> 00:39:39,110
What Sword Spirit?

898
00:39:39,150 --> 00:39:40,710
Master, don't you know?

899
00:39:40,730 --> 00:39:41,450
Shut up.

900
00:39:41,940 --> 00:39:42,750
Master,

901
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:45,160
isn't he traveling around the world?

902
00:39:46,100 --> 00:39:47,070
I was wrong.

903
00:39:47,510 --> 00:39:48,630
Please forgive me.

904
00:39:50,060 --> 00:39:51,260
You may leave.
